comments: Dort (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm at the end of the drive that causes him to lose the ball.
Murphy III (NOP) reaches around Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and marginal contact occurs with his off-arm during the driving shot attempt.
Hayes (NOP) establishes himself and firms up over his right foot in Dort's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs to his side as he navigates over the pick.
Dort (OKC) reaches in and marginal arm contact occurs with Ingram (NOP) as the two come together during the drive.
Dort (OKC) establishes himself in McCollum's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Hayes (NOP) moves into Williams' (OKC) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) slides alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal body contact during the driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) grabs and holds Valanciunas' (NOP) arm and the contact affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Giddey (OKC).
Williams (OKC) reaches in and initiates contact with Valanciunas' (NOP) arm that affects his SQBR.
Dort (OKC) swipes across and initiates illegal contact with Ingram's (NOP) head as he receives the pass.
Richardson (NOP) briefly places his arm on Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) shoulder and marginal contact occurs as Richardson cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Marshall (NOP) reaches in and initiates contact with Dort's (OKC) arm that affects his SQBR after he secures the loose ball.
Dort (OKC) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
